            <div class="subsection-content col-content" data-au="flex-container flex-vertical small-gap">
              <p>While there are plenty of global issues that need fixing, in looking at the United Nation's Sustainable Development Goals, our work most closely aligns with <a class="text-link" href="https://sdgs.un.org/goals/goal4" target="_blank" aria-label="SDG 4 (opens in new window)">Quality Education (4)</a>, <a class="text-link" href="https://sdgs.un.org/goals/goal13" target="_blank" aria-label="SDG 13 (opens in new window)">Climate Action (13)</a>, <a class="text-link" href="https://sdgs.un.org/goals/goal14" target="_blank" aria-label="SDG 14 (opens in new window)">Life Below Water (14)</a>, and <a class="text-link" href="https://sdgs.un.org/goals/goal15" target="_blank" aria-label="SDG 15 (opens in new window)">Life on Land (15)</a>. Each project fits within the UN's SDGs a bit differently, but these are at the base of everything we do.</p>
              <p>Looking for our commitments to Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion? Read our DEI statement <a class="text-link" href="/legal/dei">here</a>.</p>
