            <div class="subsection-content col-content" data-au="flex-container flex-vertical small-gap">
              <p>Most of our goals revolve around getting X project done by Y, but we are committed to running our company sustainably as well. Our largest goal is to run entirely on renewable energy (and effectively, being carbon-free) by 2035, but even now, we are taking steps to limiting our impact. Since 2024, a portion of our electricity is sourced from our solar array, all of our websites are hosted using renewable energy providers, we even save bound-for-e-waste devices and parts to use in our operations!</p>
              <p>To see a full list of our corporate sustainability goals, visit our <a class="text-link" href="https://profiles.eco/terrabyte" target="_blank" aria-label="Terrabyte dot Eco profile (opens in new window)">.Eco Profile</a>.</p>
